{"title":"论文提交的规则怪谈","uid":"bb14fa6d0d609ec878ff68d6cd6879be","slug":"paperSubmission","date":"2025-09-27T16:00:00.000Z","updated":"2025-12-30T01:45:16.583Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/paperSubmission.json","keywords":null,"cover":"/img/ICLR logo.png","content":"<ol>\n<li><p>一般来说DDL会往后延迟半小时，但不可寄希望于这半小时。</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>整理附件材料的时候，请务必注意源码中的path路径是否全部替换，同时严查是否存在log日志，如果发现，请立刻删除。</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>论文reference的bibtex检查是否存在以下四个关键关键字，示例：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bibtex\" data-language=\"bibtex\"><code class=\"language-bibtex\">@article&#123;aggarwal2025l1,\n  title&#x3D;&#123;L1: Controlling how long a reasoning model thinks with reinforcement learning&#125;,\n  author&#x3D;&#123;Aggarwal, Pranjal and Welleck, Sean&#125;,\n  journal&#x3D;&#123;arXiv preprint arXiv:2503.04697&#125;,\n  year&#x3D;&#123;2025&#125;\n&#125;</code></pre>\n\n<p>​4. rebuttal的时候先冷静下来，从审稿人的角度去思考为什么他会这么问，然后再回答。同时rebuttal的内容对于自己所说的内容一定要有理有据，就如果有神人问起来，也要能够回答的出来，而非只是凭感觉。</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n","feature":false,"text":" 一般来说DDL会往后延迟半小时，但不可寄希望于这半小时。 整理附件材料的时候，请务必注意源码中的path路径是否全部替换，同时严查是否存在log日志，如果发现，请立刻删除。 论文reference的bibtex检查是否存在以下四个关键关键字，示例： @article&#123;...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":529,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"paper","slug":"paper","count":1,"path":"api/categories/paper.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"规则怪谈","slug":"规则怪谈","count":1,"path":"api/tags/规则怪谈.json"},{"name":"submission","slug":"submission","count":1,"path":"api/tags/submission.json"},{"name":"paper","slug":"paper","count":1,"path":"api/tags/paper.json"}],"toc":"","author":{"name":"Ausert","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"/img/Ausert.jpg","link":"/","description":"tech otakus save the world","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/AusertDream","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{"bilibili":{"icon":"/svg/bilibili.svg","link":"https://space.bilibili.com/102368527?spm_id_from=333.1007.0.0"},"codeforce":{"icon"